  "frontCover": "Front cover of a birthday greeting card, 9:16 ratio, in a charming watercolor style with visible brushstrokes and organic paint bleeds. The scene features a cheerful, round cartoon character wearing an apron, holding a fork and a platter piled high with various delicious food items including sushi, pizza slices, a cupcake, and what appears to be fried chicken or breaded items. The character has a warm, wide smile and closed eyes. Behind him, two other stylized cartoon characters are visible: one with red hair and glasses holding a camera, and another with dark hair and glasses. The background suggests an outdoor setting with hints of a building and an awning in a soft blue color. The overall color palette is warm and inviting, dominated by yellows, oranges, and browns, with touches of blue and green. The text \"Happy Birthday, Mau!\" is prominently displayed at the top in a playful, flowing, handwritten cursive script, colored in a warm brown. The overall mood is lighthearted, humorous, and celebratory, perfectly capturing the joy of a birthday feast.",
