  "rightInterior": "Right interior panel of a birthday greeting card, 9:16 ratio, in a cohesive watercolor style with soft, flowing colors, visible brushstrokes, and organic paint bleeds. This panel beautifully integrates the birthday message into a creative and artistic design, without any people. The background is a soft, warm wash of yellow and orange watercolor, with subtle, abstract shapes that hint at festive elements or perhaps even stylized food motifs from the front cover, rendered with delicate brushwork. The main focus is the handwritten message: \"Dearest Mau, Watching you paint the world with your beautiful spirit is the greatest gift, and today, we celebrate the incredible artist and person you are. Your life is a masterpiece, and I feel so lucky to have a place in the gallery of your heart. I hope your special day is as full and wonderful as the feast we're about to enjoy! All my love, Meiling\". The text is presented in an elegant, flowing, handwritten cursive script, in a warm brown color, with a natural ink-like appearance and slight variations in line weight, suggesting genuine warmth and personality. The handwriting is clear, legible, and graceful. The message is surrounded by delicate, abstract watercolor flourishes that frame it artistically, avoiding clichÃ©s and creating a unique, heartfelt presentation. The overall mood is warm, personal, and celebratory, serving as the emotional climax of the card."
